        code .table
        |  to any
        code table
        | . It may seem super redundant, but given the widespread use of tables for other plugins like calendars and date pickers, we've opted to isolate our custom table styles.
      .table-responsive
        table.table
          thead
            tr
              th #
              th First Name
              th Last Name
              th Username
          tbody
            tr
